# Coding Style

Follow [`docs/project-conventions.md`](../../docs/project-conventions.md) and [`README.md`](../../README.md).

- TypeScript strict mode; Prettier + ESLint enforced in CI.
- Conventional Commits; minimal focused diffs.
- Match existing naming: `camelCase` variables, `PascalCase` components/classes, kebab-case doc filenames.
- Update relevant `docs/` when behavior or API contracts change.
